About GINGER Goa Panjim

Offering the 'Ginger Promise', Ginger Goa is a beautiful property with plenty of recreational options and comfortable facilities enriched by a contemporary ambience.

  • Keep your little ones engaged in the safe play area within the premises. 
  • Chillout at the lounge with a book or play foosball with loved ones. 
  • Enjoy a lively ambience at Cafe Et Cetera with your drink or relish global delicacies at The Square Meal Restaurant.

Property Rules

Check-in: 2 PMCheck-out: 12 PM

Couple, Bachelor Rules Couple Friendly

Unmarried couples/guests with Local IDs are allowed.

Guests with fever are not allowed
PAN Card, Office ID and Non-Govt IDs are not accepted as ID proof(s)
Passport, Aadhar, Driving License and Govt. ID are accepted as ID proof(s)
Property staff is trained on hygiene guidelines
Pets are not allowed.
Smoking within the premises is not allowed
Allows private parties or events
Quarantine protocols are being followed as per local government authorities
Read All Property Rules

Child & Extra Bed Policy

  • No extra bed will be provided to accommodate any child included in the booking.
  • An extra bed will be provided to accommodate any additional guest included in the booking for a charge mentioned below.
  • INR 1500 will be charged for an extra mattress per guest. (To be paid at the property)
